{"tid":1981264,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愛之道，愛人之道","createTime":"2020-04-20T14:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T17:06:10.000Z","uid":256362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bde446ae1834bf87efe1b9d7b79ebfba866a11d6","tid":1981264,"uid":256362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:33:15.000Z","msg":"見呢個世道太多即食，想修行愛人之道。<br />\n<br />\n鍾意人好多時好多因素決定，非理性，ok。<br />\n但拍拖，經營感情/愛情係有得自己控制，想知道大家/父母/識嘅人點樣維繫一段長長久久嘅關係呢？腿張開/含/奶/扑咗先一齊嗰啲麻煩左上角出去thx<br />\n<br />\n磚:<br />\n(對自己)<br />\n1. 愛自己，理解自己需要<br />\n2. 不斷進修自己，令今日嘅我好過昨日嘅我，今日學識痾屎壓水花、放屁較靜音都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 加強控制誘惑/心動嘅行動，唔好有食唔食<br />\n<br />\n(對對方)<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪乜尻柒閪屎都發腺氣</span></span></strong><br />\n2. 冷靜溝通表達自己感受、所需<br />\n3. 設身處地企對方角度思考🤔<br />\n4. 不輕易說分手<br />\n5. 信，但留有一手<br />\n6. 男女互畀驚喜/小禮物 eg. 買咗份禮物收埋咗喺你屋企，你自己搵啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求玉。"},{"pid":"86f7508c5266451df9c6db32c4697db7b2069175","tid":1981264,"uid":256362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57afedc61e1b94ec168ddf9f6475d607c3104ce0","tid":1981264,"uid":256362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07ee5eacbad506a26927e5479d434aee6352bb33","tid":1981264,"uid":256362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:34:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a033b521efb1f267a2e5a2fa12b4f5efb18353f","tid":1981264,"uid":256362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc5f93a092215bbc05387d77e57d00005924f80b","tid":1981264,"uid":256362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ab7522c026b7c91f990bd8620e6bc77f3818d41","tid":1981264,"uid":256362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"